cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.NE, cs.SD, cs.MA

The paper presents a deep learning-based approach for walking speed estimation using smartphone sensors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the potential applications of the proposed approach in various fields such as health-care and transportation, indicating a possible fit with cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.NE (Neuroscience). The paper also involves experiments with participants, suggesting a possible fit with cs.SD (Sound) and cs.MA (Measurement and Instrumentation).
